{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858935202,"sessionID":"ses_2868f772dffedk9WSHy9p19eik","part":{"id":"prt_d7970df6e001nGkZAAHuzyvHq8","messageID":"msg_d7970ced3001DiAhntWf6kgH4V","sessionID":"ses_2868f772dffedk9WSHy9p19eik","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_36d451256f774b54b83fdf02","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"ls -la /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/","description":"List workloadmanager directory"},"output":"total 152\ndrwxr-xr-x 8 root root  4096 Apr 11 02:54 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 7 root root  4096 Apr 11 03:13 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  1139 Apr 11 01:18 config.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  2445 Apr 11 01:18 config_test.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root   696 Apr 11 02:50 defaults.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 20585 Apr 11 01:41 delta-spec.md\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 34947 Apr 11 01:15 design.md\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  4012 Apr 11 02:53 garbage_collector.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  6202 Apr 11 04:39 garbage_collector_test.go\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:47 handler\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:29 middleware\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:52 processor\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 17940 Apr 11 02:22 proposal.md\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 02:39 reconciler\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:18 response\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  1993 Apr 11 02:56 routes.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  2499 Apr 11 01:29 routes_test.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  2140 Apr 11 01:23 server.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  1437 Apr 11 01:29 server_test.go\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:45 types\n","metadata":{"output":"total 152\ndrwxr-xr-x 8 root root  4096 Apr 11 02:54 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 7 root root  4096 Apr 11 03:13 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  1139 Apr 11 01:18 config.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  2445 Apr 11 01:18 config_test.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root   696 Apr 11 02:50 defaults.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 20585 Apr 11 01:41 delta-spec.md\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 34947 Apr 11 01:15 design.md\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  4012 Apr 11 02:53 garbage_collector.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  6202 Apr 11 04:39 garbage_collector_test.go\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:47 handler\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:29 middleware\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:52 processor\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 17940 Apr 11 02:22 proposal.md\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 02:39 reconciler\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:18 response\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  1993 Apr 11 02:56 routes.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  2499 Apr 11 01:29 routes_test.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  2140 Apr 11 01:23 server.go\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  1437 Apr 11 01:29 server_test.go\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root  4096 Apr 11 01:45 types\n","exit":0,"description":"List workloadmanager directory","truncated":false},"title":"List workloadmanager directory","time":{"start":1775858935190,"end":1775858935201}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858935206,"sessionID":"ses_2868f772dffedk9WSHy9p19eik","part":{"id":"prt_d7970d905001G76v122Hn5V4MS","messageID":"msg_d7970ced3001DiAhntWf6kgH4V","sessionID":"ses_2868f772dffedk9WSHy9p19eik","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_264983bf6783426c9a5f3f93","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md","limit":80},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 completed |\n12: \n13: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架提供 Kubernetes-native 的 HTTP API，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载。该服务封装了 client-go 的复杂性，为 Python SDK、CLI 工具和其他消费者提供简化的 RESTful 接口。\n14: \n15: ## Architecture\n16: \n17: ### 组件分层\n18: \n19: ```\n20: Client (SDK/CLI/Frontend)\n21:   ↓ HTTPS\n22: Gin Router (:8080)\n23:   ↓\n24: Middleware Stack\n25:   ├─ LoggingMiddleware\n26:   ├─ RecoveryMiddleware\n27:   ├─ CORSMiddleware\n28:   └─ AuthMiddleware (optional)\n29:   ↓\n30: HTTP Handlers\n31:   ├─ AgentRuntime Handlers\n32:   ├─ CodeInterpreter Handlers\n33:   ├─ Health Handlers\n34:   └─ Metrics Handler\n35:   ↓\n36: Service Layer (WorkloadManager Interface)\n37:   ↓\n38: Kubernetes Client Layer\n39:   ├─ typed client (AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface)\n40:   ├─ informers (SharedInformerFactory)\n41:   └─ listers (AgentRuntimeLister, CodeInterpreterLister)\n42:   ↓\n43: Kubernetes API Server\n44: ```\n45: \n46: ### 目录结构\n47: \n48: ```\n49: pkg/workloadmanager/\n50: ├── server.go              # Gin server setup, router configuration, graceful shutdown\n51: ├── service.go             # WorkloadManager interface definition\n52: ├── client.go              # Kubernetes client initialization\n53: ├── types.go               # API request/response DTOs\n54: ├── handlers/\n55: │   ├── agentruntime.go    # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n56: │   ├── codeinterpreter.go # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n57: │   ├── health.go          # Health check handlers (/healthz, /readyz)\n58: │   └── metrics.go         # Prometheus metrics handler\n59: ├── middleware/\n60: │   ├── auth.go            # JWT/Kubernetes TokenReview authentication\n61: │   ├── logging.go         # Request logging\n62: │   └── error.go           # Centralized error handling\n63: └── store/\n64:     └── store.go           # Store interface (Redis-backed)\n65: ```\n66: \n67: ### 启动流程\n68: \n69: ```go\n70: main():\n71:   1. LoadConfig() — 从环境变量和 flags 加载配置\n72:   2. NewK8sClient() — 初始化 Kubernetes clientset\n73:   3. NewSharedInformerFactory() — 创建 informer factory\n74:   4. RegisterInformers() — 注册 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter informers\n75:   5. StartInformers() — 启动 informers 并等待 cache sync\n76:   6. NewWorkloadManager() — 初始化 service layer\n77:   7. NewServer() — 创建 Gin server\n78:   8. RegisterRoutes() — 注册 HTTP routes\n79:   9. StartServer() — 监听端口，阻塞直到 shutdown\n80: ```\n\n(Showing lines 1-80 of 1135. Use offset=81 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 completed |\n\nWorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架提供 Kubernetes-native 的 HTTP API，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载。该服务封装了 client-go 的复杂性，为 Python SDK、CLI 工具和其他消费者提供简化的 RESTful 接口。\n\n## Architecture\n\n### 组件分层\n\n```\nClient (SDK/CLI/Frontend)","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md","time":{"start":1775858935185,"end":1775858935204}}}}
